# üß† AWS MLOps ‚Äî Diabetes Prediction

A simple demo showing **end-to-end MLOps on AWS** using **S3, SageMaker, and Gradio**.  
The project trains a model, uploads it to S3, deploys it as an endpoint, and provides a web UI for predictions.

---

## ‚öôÔ∏è Steps

### 1Ô∏è‚É£ Train & Upload Model
```bash
python train_upload_model.py
````

Trains a Linear Regression model and uploads it to your S3 bucket.

### 2Ô∏è‚É£ Deploy to SageMaker

```bash
python deploy_model.py
```

Deploys the model as a SageMaker endpoint.

### 3Ô∏è‚É£ Test Locally

Use Gradio for easy predictions:

```bash
python gradio_app.py
```

